OL,3,CNew 'pilot' nursery set up in Jersey
OL,5,FA new government-run nursery will open
OL,6,Ffor two and three year olds with
OL,7,Fadditional needs in Jersey.
OL,9,FStarting in October, the pilot scheme
OL,10,Fat d'Auverge School in St Helier may
OL,11,Flead to similar sites opening within
OL,12,Fother state primary schools if
OL,13,Fsuccessful.
OL,15,FEducation Minister Deputy Rob Ward
OL,16,Fexplains: "I'm delighted that we are
OL,17,Fable to offer this provision to
OL,18,Fparents and families in the coming
OL,19,Fweeks."
