OL,3,CNew 'pilot' nursery set up in Jersey
OL,5,FHe adds: "It is the first step and one
OL,6,Fof a number of possible options we're
OL,7,Flooking at to achieve the universal
OL,8,Foffer for two to three year olds."
OL,10,FThe Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,11,FFarnham, has pledged to offer free
OL,12,Fnursery care to all children in this
OL,13,Fage group by the end of the current
OL,14,Fpolitical term in 2026.
OL,16,FThe headteacher of d'Auvergne, Sam
OL,17,FCooper, adds: "We're very happy to
OL,18,Fsupport the pilot in any way we can
OL,19,Fand we look forward to welcoming more
OL,20,Fchildren into our wider school
OL,21,Fcommunity."
